HEADWORD: Thilk
<hw>Thilk</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>pron.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Ilk</er>
same.]</ety> <def>That same; this; that.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧I love <xex>thilk</xex> lass.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou spake right now of <qex>thilke</qex> traitor death.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thill</ent>⟦br⟧
